ISLAMABAD, Feb 5 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Saturday wished President of Turkey Recep Tayyip Erdogan and his wife Emine Erdogan swift and complete recovery from COVID 19.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “I just learnt that my brother Recep Tayyip Erdogan, President of Turkey and Madame Emine Erdogan tested positive for Covid-19 Omicron. On behalf of our government, the people of Pakistan and on my own behalf I wish them a swift and complete recovery.”
